.TH TETHER-GTK 1 "May 2026" "Tether 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tether-gtk \- Graphical interface for Tether
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tether-gtk
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tether-gtk
is a GTK-based graphical application for managing Tether connections and devices.
It provides a user-friendly interface to:
.IP \(bu 2
Monitor the status of the connection to the Tether daemon.
.IP \(bu 2
Manage paired devices and accept new pairing requests.
.IP \(bu 2
Send and receive files.
.IP \(bu 2
View clipboard sync history and status.
.PP
If the \fBtetherd\fR(8) daemon is not running, \fBtether-gtk\fR will attempt to
start it automatically.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR tether (1),
.BR tetherd (8)
